Package com.flightbookings.flight_bookings.models

Class Seat

java.lang.Object
com.flightbookings.flight_bookings.models.Seat
@Entity public class Seat extends Object
Represents a seat entity in the system. Contains details about the seat's row, letter, booking status, and associations with flights and bookings.
